@matanSF You know, the best customer to get is the one you already have. I watched Craig Newmark do customer service all night long, and I watched many other great people do customer service while working at Rackspace and elsewhere. 

When you keep customers, you grow faster. If you're good at keeping a customer, they're going to find you other customers. Conversely, if you don't keep your customers, they don't tell other people about you. 

This is the way a company grows faster: by providing better customer service.

